data.description: Charming Single Story Home located on a Cul de sac with backyard access. This home offers a open floorplan, kitchen with ample counter space and cabinets. And Large bedrooms with walk in closets.  The backyard has three storage sheds that will convey with the property. Lots of room for family gatherings.  Refrigerated AC to help keep you cool. Part of the garage has been converted to a room.   A Great Place to Call Home!
